      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"7. SUTTON JAZZ put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Shrewd (25.60) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can go on with it. 6. TAW UNBOUND missed the frame on debut when fifth (30.82) at Wentworth Park over 520m. Much improved and rates a winning chance. 2. TAW ACTIVATE failed to threaten in two average runs to date. A forward showing wouldn’t surprise. 3. OVATION KEY gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.\",\"runners\":[7,6,2,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
